      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## The whole pipeline on one screen \u2014 99 cabinets to ClickHouse in seconds.\n\nEvery device in all 99 cabinets emits CloudEvents onto its cabinet's NATS JetStream buffer; leaf-node replication carries them up regional \u2192 central \u2192 DMZ tiers, and a batching sink lands them in each DOT's ClickHouse. Ingest rate, per-cabinet freshness, events by service, and NATS tier liveness move together here \u2014 the live heartbeat of the whole federated network on one page."
      }
    },
